Get all ZIP codes that fall within a given congressional district

Source: R/zip_lookups.r
cd_to_zip.Rd

Get all ZIP codes that fall within a given congressional district

cd_to_zip(state_fips_code, congressional_district)

Arguments

state_fips_code

A two-digit U.S. FIPS code for a state
congressional_district

A two digit number specifying a congressional district in a given

Value

dataframe of all congressional districts found for given ZIP code, including state code

Examples

cd_to_zip('34','03')
